31 SECTION 5. EMERGENCY CLAUSE. It is found and determined by the
32 General Assembly of the State of Arkansas that the percentage of Arkansas's
33 elderly population is increasing; that food insecurity within Arkansas's
34 elderly population is also increasing; that if unaddressed, this food
35 insecurity will continue to worsen and lead to needless mental and physical
36 suffering and increased financial stress; that this act creates the Fight
